<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.9">
<l>pārai yūrum pāran tīrap pārttaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>tērai yūrun tēva tēvaṉ cērumūr</l>
<l>tārai yūrun taṇta ḷirvēli puṭaicūḻa</l>
<l>nārai yūrum nalva yalcūḻnta naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city which belongs to the god of gods who mounted</l>
<l>Pārtha’s chariot to end the burdens which mounted on the earth,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr, surrounded by fine fields where herons creep,</l>
<l>As hedges surround on [all] sides with new shoots</l>
<l rend="indent">where a flow [of nectar] spreads.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
